                    <span>This book do exactly what it states - deconstruct 50 of the best websites HOMEPAGES. It does not go into detail about the inner pages or usability errors other then those which appear at the first page.<p>Jakob explanations are clear, written well and to-the-point, and the way the book is presented is admirable.<p>Get this book for the ability to point and fix any usability issue on any homepage you will ever visit/build.</span>
                  
              
